{"tid":905091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女童拒打預防針　男老師被她狠踢生殖器好興奮","createTime":"2018-11-17T00:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T03:38:58.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e2f0b9c481686873627c51b001538c6a74e95043","tid":905091,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:52:13.000Z","msg":"印尼一間小學教室內，有一名女童拒打預防針，不只在保健室內大哭大鬧，甚至抗拒到當場狠踢男老師的下體，讓男老師當場痛不欲生。<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，相信該班正在接受預防針注射，但這名小女生相當抗拒，老師無奈追著她跑，並把她抱住，試圖安撫女童，希望她能乖乖接受注射。但沒想到女童不僅大哭大鬧，還一腳狠踹老師的生殖器部位，讓老師感受到人生最痛的一刻。但老師並沒有責罵女童，也沒有擺出臭臉，反而露出興奮的笑容。女童之後掙脫老師逃跑，最後未知女童是否成功接受預防針注射。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181117/640_1e154a4937621a26c48a029a9e5de18d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181117%2F640_1e154a4937621a26c48a029a9e5de18d.jpg&h=eace3267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女童拒打預防針，男老師被她狠踢生殖器。翻自《每日郵報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181117/640_2cbc018c0f5c9b53deb3233a2c9bda6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181117%2F640_2cbc018c0f5c9b53deb3233a2c9bda6f.jpg&h=05bba3b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老師企圖安撫女童。翻自《每日郵報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181117/640_b02a37e2e5365eb0cc9b8f4f9df7d48b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181117%2F640_b02a37e2e5365eb0cc9b8f4f9df7d48b.jpg&h=8a208639&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但老師依舊被女童狠踢下體，一度露出興奮嗨笑表情。翻自《每日郵報》<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181117/1468053/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181117%2F1468053%2F&d=8z4ar%2F7dxXsMaV4BHpo%2B74zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e59e5abc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181117%2F1468053%2F&h=07c29590\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181117/1468053/</a>"},{"pid":"a92ec2d15ecd140546226c18e7a1e0ab779ad13e","tid":905091,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:53:41.000Z","msg":"sosad 樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbfee1e56d7d50910a193205f1408b114b5f75f","tid":905091,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:54:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0ecc10f9675f5db54c00cdce6caa1e6c8567dd1","tid":905091,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:56:37.000Z","msg":"老師有冇射到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d85e99f48a42da347ebd2779aedd240f5c20d4","tid":905091,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:02:49.000Z","msg":"M<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab68de9207cdff7974d01aac6a296919dffe1c66","tid":905091,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:05:55.000Z","msg":"個老師坐低都未講野就踢落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0d83fb535b9e03bce67798d5d9cf03bd25c31d","tid":905091,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab68de9207cdff7974d01aac6a296919dffe1c66","tid":905091,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:05:55.000Z","msg":"個老師坐低都未講野就踢落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345a2c290d4b5e1a628138defb309d52e5f035eb","tid":905091,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"一度露出興奮嗨笑表情<img src=\"/assets/faces/no